Leonard Green May Bid for BJ’s Wholesale Today, N.Y. Post Says

-- B y   A l a n   P u r k i s s
-- 
2011-04-13T06:55:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-13/leonard-green-may-bid-for-bj-s-wholesale-today-n-y-post-says.html
Leonard Green & Partners LP, a U.S.
buyout firm, is likely to make an opening-round offer today for
regional warehouse chain  BJ’s Wholesale Club Inc. (BJ) , the New York
Post reported, citing unidentified people familiar with the
matter.   Bidders picked for the second round will probably be asked
to make binding offers by the end of May, the newspaper said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
